This version does work. For you people that have trouble installing (not mounting) try installing in safe mode. After you've installed check this list for servers: http://blizzhackers.com/viewforum.php?f=163&sid=4bce21a12666716fa5b4ee10b93dbfbe . Patch to desired server version. The newest patch for now is patch 1.2.4. To get it just log on to the normal blizzard server and type in a fake account for example name:aaa pass:xxx . Before you log in to any private server don't forget to delete your WDB folder or you and others around your spawn point WILL CRASH! (There are tools to delete it for you) Email me or talk to me on msn at bjorn_ejvald@hotmail.com if you have any questions. I cannot, i repeat CANNOT help you with error #132 or error #0 so don't ask me or i WILL block you.
